        comparaisonTransport: "The Baia bus line 1 connects Arcachon to the Dune du Pilat in 20-30 min for €1.30 (limited frequency off-season). The TaxiNeo taxi at €15 — €20 is door-to-door in 10 min. Ideal for families. Saves the paid Dune car park fee (€6-10).",
